Author: petaldust
Text: mannnnnn lean cuisine is my shit. but my cap for frozen meals is 300 calls so every time i see the ziti one i just whisper to it “someday...” and then get my stupid sad cheese ravioli bc it’s 250.

Author: TotallyNotARadar
Text: Lean Cuisines are the shit. They were all my mom ever bought growing up which was weird but I was always so excited when she let me have one for dinner because I thought they were fancy
